Step by step curly style guide using the one and only @kevin.murphy 

1. EVERLASTING.COLOUR WASH 
Wash thoroughly through hair on scalp, don’t emphasize too much on the rest of hair as you will strip your curls.

2.  KILLER.CURLS RINSE 
Leave in for 1-2 minutes to get that deep treatment effect. This will help the softness and bounce of your curls. A must on wash days!

3. LEAVE-IN.REPAIR 
Apply ONLY to your scalp. This really relieves my hair of frizz and you only need a little

4.  EASY.RIDER 
Run through your curls and scrunch while wet!

Side note: the more product you use the heavier your hair will be, the less product the lighter your hair will be!
